devdoc.details: Exponentiation and logarithm functions for 18 decimal fixed point numbers (both base and exponent/argument). Exponentiation and logarithm with arbitrary bases (x^y and log_x(y)) are implemented by conversion to natural exponentiation and logarithm (where the base is Euler's number).
